<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dental X-ray Disease Detection</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: #f8fafc;
            color: #2d3748;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1e40af);
            color: white;
            padding: 120px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cpath d='M30 30h1v1h-1z' fill='rgba(255,255,255,0.1)'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            opacity: 0.2;
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -50px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 100px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            clip-path: polygon(0 50%, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease-out;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(37,99,235,0.2);
        }

        .problem-statement {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #1e40af;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
            padding: 30px;
            border-left: none;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #f0f7ff, #ffffff);
            position: relative;
        }

        .solution {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .benefit-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 4px solid #2563eb;
        }

        .benefit-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(37,99,235,0.2);
        }

        .benefit-card h3 {
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .benefit-card h3::before {
            content: '⚕';
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
            color: #1e40af;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #2563eb;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Dental X-ray Disease Detection</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
            Revolutionizing Dental Diagnostics with AI Technology
        </p>
    </section>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="problem-statement card">
            "Traditional dental disease detection methods are time-consuming and prone to human error, leading to delayed diagnoses and potential oversight of critical conditions."
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title">Our Solution</h2>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3 style="color: #1e40af; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.8rem;">
                <span style="margin-right: 10px;">⚕</span>Advanced AI Analysis
            </h3>
            <p>
                Our system leverages cutting-edge machine learning algorithms to analyze dental X-ray images, 
                automatically detecting and classifying various dental conditions with unprecedented accuracy. 
                By combining deep learning techniques with extensive dental imaging expertise, we've created a 
                revolutionary tool for modern dental professionals.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="solution">
            <div class="benefit-card">
                <h3>Enhanced Accuracy</h3>
                <p>
                    Our ML model achieves over 95% accuracy in detecting dental diseases, significantly 
                    reducing the risk of misdiagnosis and ensuring more reliable treatment planning.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="benefit-card">
                <h3>Time Efficiency</h3>
                <p>
                    Automated analysis reduces diagnosis time from hours to minutes, allowing dental 
                    professionals to focus more on patient care and treatment planning.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const cards = document.querySelectorAll('.card, .benefit-card');
        const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                    entry.target.style.opacity = 1;
                    entry.target.style.transform = 'translateY(0)';
                }
            });
        });

        cards.forEach(card => {
            card.style.opacity = 0;
            card.style.transform = 'translateY(20px)';
            card.style.transition = 'all 0.6s ease-out';
            observer.observe(card);
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>